snippet.title: Diana and Roma Fun Playtime at Warner Bros. World Amusement Park Abu Dhabi
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma with their parents have fun at the Warner Bros. World Amusement Park Abu Dhabi – the world’s biggest indoor theme park!
The park has six interactive spaces. Each of the zones has its own design and special effects, as well as its own themed restaurants. All rides are made in the style of the original Warner Bros. studio scenery, making you feel like a real superhero!
